address: 21 Digital-ro 37na-gil, Daerim 2(i)-dong, Yeongdeungpo-gu, Seoul, South Korea
83 Achasan-ro, Seongsu-dong 2(i)-ga, Seongdong-gu, Seoul, South Korea
description: Cube Entertainment is an entertainment company established by Hong Shengcheng, the former president of JYP. The company is located in Cheongdam-dong, Gangnam District, not far from JYP. Now the company's well-known artists include 4Minute and BEAST. It is said that there are often celebrities coming and going here. If you like Hallyu, you can go here to follow Korean stars. The cafe opposite CUBE is a good place to stay, and there are often entertainers who come to have coffee.

address: 45 Saemunan-ro, Sajik-dong, Jongno-gu, Seoul, South Korea
description: The 400-year-old Gyeonghui Palace was virtually destroyed during the Japanese colonial period, leaving only a few of the original elements. A handful remain, however, and are worth a visit. Highlights include the carvings of dragons' heads, stone stairways, and a beautiful garden surrounding the palace.
